title: No, Jove. Desantis didn't tell Paden "Go On Yourself "
subtitle: The Governor of Florida expressed dissatisfaction with the possible travel restrictions imposed on COVID-19, but not in many words.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: (Florida Goff) Ron Desantes responded to the possibility of imposing travel restrictions on COVID-19 by telling US President Joe Baiden, "Go fuck yourself" during a conference call in February 2021.
